# Lưu ý: set giá trị {{AuthToken}} = access token (Bearer). Nếu chưa có token, thực hiện flow đăng nhập/verify-otp để lấy token.
###

### Get current user's permissions
GET {{MovieReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/permissions/me
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get permissions of a role (replace {roleId})
GET {{MovieReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/permissions/roles/{roleId}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Accept: application/json

###
### Add permission to a role
POST {{MovieReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/permissions/roles/{roleId}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permission": "Permission.Payments.Create"
}

###

### Remove permission from a role
DELETE {{MovieReservation.Server_HostAddress}}/api/permissions/roles/{roleId}
Authorization: Bearer {{AuthToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "permission": "Permission.Payments.Create"
}

